Gary Bond https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gary_Bond 0 Gary James Bond (7 February 1940 – 12 October 1995) was an English actor and singer. He is known for his roles in several high profile West End plays and musicals, as well as his portrayal of protagonist John Grant in the 1971 cult Australian film Wake in Fright.
